1D949B81AE44659084DBFBEAE6EB20\" title=\"gz****s\" target=\"_blank\">gz****s</a></span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li class=\"title cf\">\r\n				<span class=\"f_left\"><span itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Rating\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" class=\"starlist\"> <span style=\"width:100%;\"> </span></span> <span class=\"sblockline\"> 景色：5?\r\n                                                    趣味：5?\r\n                                                    性价比：4?\r\n                                                &nbsp; </span> </span> <span class=\"f_right\">建议游览6小时</span> <span class=\"youcate\"> 2015-7&nbsp;出游 </span> \r\n			</li>\r\n			<li itemprop=\"description\" class=\"main_con\">\r\n				<span class=\"heightbox\">一般游<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/guilin28/2888.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_67690337_28_sid2888_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"75898\" data-type=\"3\">漓江</a>的主要方式有坐船、竹筏及徒步，其中坐船又有分<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/resort/guilin28/137416.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_67690337_28_sid137416_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"98751\" data-type=\"6\">漓江精华游</a>、<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/yangshuo702.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_67690337_702_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"527\" data-type=\"4\">阳朔</a>水上游、市区水上游（<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/guilin28.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_67690337_28_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"28\" data-type=\"4\">桂林</a>市\r\n区），漓江风景如画，江水流速缓慢，很适合照相。这次游玩是从磨盘山码头上船去阳朔的，较早就从市区出发去码头，9点多才开船，中间历时5-6小时。船上\r\n的中餐非常差，实在是贵又不好吃，建议来游玩的朋友自己带些零食，随便吃点，自己照相，不要参加船上照相的，感觉他们照的背景是合成的。坐船游漓江玩的还\r\n是很开心的。</span> \r\n			</li>\r\n			<li class=\"comment_piclist cf\">\r\n				<a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g4/M04/DB/38/CggYHVZfnpSAC-XXABGVz0L62xE465.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/DB/38/CggYHVZfnpSAC-XXABGVz0L62xE465_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/DB/38/CggYHVZfnpSAC-XXABGVz0L62xE465_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg01.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g4/M04/DB/38/CggYHVZfnpSAC-XXABGVz0L62xE465_C_90_90.jpg\" /></a> <a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g3/M00/BA/08/CggYGlZfnpCAUw9wABNA0-tikxo088.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/BA/08/CggYGlZfnpCAUw9wABNA0-tikxo088_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/BA/08/CggYGlZfnpCAUw9wABNA0-tikxo088_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg08.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/BA/08/CggYGlZfnpCAUw9wABNA0-tikxo088_C_90_90.jpg\" /></a> <a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g3/M06/D0/EB/CggYG1ZfnoyAHI35ABfRWs42VyY900.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M06/D0/EB/CggYG1ZfnoyAHI35ABfRWs42VyY900_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M06/D0/EB/CggYG1ZfnoyAHI35ABfRWs42VyY900_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg05.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M06/D0/EB/CggYG1ZfnoyAHI35ABfRWs42VyY900_C_90_90.jpg\" /></a> <a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g3/M00/D2/C8/CggYGVZfnomAfoaKABreqv-mmRQ929.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/D2/C8/CggYGVZfnomAfoaKABreqv-mmRQ929_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/D2/C8/CggYGVZfnomAfoaKABreqv-mmRQ929_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M00/D2/C8/CggYGVZfnomAfoaKABreqv-mmRQ929_C_90_90.jpg\" /></a> \r\n			</li>\r\n			<li class=\"from_link\">\r\n				<span class=\"f_left\"> <span class=\"time_line\"><em itemprop=\"datePublished\">2015-12-03</em></span> </span> <span class=\"f_right\"> <span class=\"useful\"><a id=\"usefultodo\" data-clicked=\"false\" data-id=\"67690337\" class=\" a_popup_login \">有用</a> （<em>13</em>）</span> </span> \r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Review\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"review\" class=\"comment_single\">\r\n		<div class=\"userimg\">\r\n			<a href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/members/862609F77A7F4F008C364F44283AB41A\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"http://images4.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/headphoto/g5/M03/15/2B/CggYr1arJLGAGWraAAESXuU3JZs534_100_100.jpg\" height=\"60\" width=\"60\" /></a> <span class=\"ellipsis\"><a itemprop=\"author\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/members/862609F77A7F4F008C364F44283AB41A\" title=\"桃子\" target=\"_blank\">桃子</a></span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li class=\"title cf\">\r\n				<span class=\"f_left\"><span itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Rating\" itemscope=\"\" itemprop=\"reviewRating\" class=\"starlist\"> <span style=\"width:80%;\"> </span></span> <span class=\"sblockline\"> 景色：5?\r\n                                                    趣味：4?\r\n                                                    性价比：4?\r\n                                                &nbsp; </span> </span> <span class=\"youcate\"> 2016-1&nbsp;出游 </span> \r\n			</li>\r\n			<li itemprop=\"description\" class=\"main_con\">\r\n				<span class=\"heightbox\">我们是从<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/guilin28.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_28_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"28\" data-type=\"4\">桂林</a>市区坐大巴到<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/yangshuo702/52584.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_702_sid52584_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"84576\" data-type=\"3\">杨堤</a>，再由杨堤坐竹筏到<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/yangshuo702/52594.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_702_sid52594_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"84577\" data-type=\"3\">九马画山</a>（所谓竹筏，就是普通的船、一船4人、最好坐前排），据导游介绍这是一段精华路线，可以看到羊蹄峰、苹果峰和九马画山、但是前两个景点不太有名所以自己根本找不到，但船夫惜字如金不会告诉你的，除非你单花钱才会讲解，坐在船上可以深切体会<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/guilin28/2888.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_28_sid2888_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"75898\" data-type=\"3\">漓江</a>水的绿、山的仙，但是会有一点冷、可以介绍的那种，坐竹筏的尽头就是九马画山了，但是很难看出九匹来，导游说，传说看出九匹的可以当总理、看出七匹的可以当状元。从竹筏上下来会乘坐一个10坐的观光车、沿途可以让司机给你指一下<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/yangshuo702/50088.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_702_sid50088_2_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"83042\" data-type=\"3\">黄布倒影</a>的地方，也就是20元人民币的图片，很可惜我们不是坐船拍的，所以不太形象，观光车下车就是<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/sight/yangshuo702/26887.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_702_sid26887_1_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"82046\" data-type=\"3\">兴坪古镇</a>、我们只是仓促的穿过小镇，到导游说的客运站集合，坐大巴大约半小时到达<a target=\"_blank\" class=\"gs_a_poi\" href=\"http://you.ctrip.com/place/yangshuo702.html#ctm_ref=gs_290510_70470559_702_l\" data-classtype=\"1\" data-id=\"527\" data-type=\"4\">阳朔</a>！</span> \r\n			</li>\r\n			<li class=\"comment_piclist cf\">\r\n				<a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g3/M0B/29/12/CggYG1arJE-AMOmFAAG3RW6x_SA636.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/29/12/CggYG1arJE-AMOmFAAG3RW6x_SA636_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/29/12/CggYG1arJE-AMOmFAAG3RW6x_SA636_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg09.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g3/M0B/29/12/CggYG1arJE-AMOmFAAG3RW6x_SA636_C_90_90.jpg\" /></a> <a href=\"http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/fd/tg/g5/M0B/15/45/CggYsVarJFCAcyHsAAE3CC23GL8935.jpg\" data-commentimg=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/15/45/CggYsVarJFCAcyHsAAE3CC23GL8935_C_560_10000.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"> <img class=\"ttd_nopic84\" src=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/15/45/CggYsVarJFCAcyHsAAE3CC23GL8935_C_90_90.jpg\" data-thumburl=\"http://dimg02.c-ctrip.com/images/fd/tg/g5/M0B/15/45/CggYsVarJFCAcyHsAAE3CC23GL8935_C_90_90.jpg\" /