g></span><span style=\"font-family:\'\';\"></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style=\"border:1pt inset black;\">\r\n									<p>\r\n										<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong>加保费用</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'\';\"></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n								</td>\r\n								<td style=\"border:1pt inset black;\">\r\n									<p>\r\n										<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong>汽车供应商提供加保服务（</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#003399;\"><strong>50</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong>元</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#003399;\"><strong>/</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong>每天），如车辆产生维修，费用在</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#003399;\"><strong>5000</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#003399;font-size:16px;\"><strong>元以下，如购买加保则无需承担费用。</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'\';\"></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n					<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\r\n						<b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">5</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">、租车手续</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">：您需要提供本人身份证、驾驶证（驾龄</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">年以上，国内驾驶执照正副本）、国内信用卡，注意驾龄不满一年不能使用该产品；</span><span style=\"font-family:\'color:black;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\r\n						<b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">6</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">、提取车辆：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">提取车辆需刷取</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\"><strong>信用卡额度</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\"><strong>20000</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\"><strong>元押金</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\"><strong>+2000</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">元</span></strong>消费交付违章押金</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">（如果单张额度不够，可以多张担保）</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">万预售权将在您还车后经核实无损坏或其他费用后解除。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">2000</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">元违章押金在您还车一个月后，经核实无违章记录，将归还至您原支付账号。如果您租车期间发生违章，租车公司会电话通知处理，如在</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">个工作日内未处理，将由租车公司代为处理。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'color:black;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\r\n						<b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">7</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">、使用凭证：</span></b><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">本人的两证一卡（第二代身份证件、国内驾驶执照正副本、国内信用卡），</span><span style=\"font-family:\'color:black;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:black;font-size:16px;\">驾龄不满一年不能使用该产品。</span><span style=\"font-family:\'color:black;\"></span>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\">\r\n						<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">详细《车辆使用规则及流程》请点击</span><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">:</span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"></span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://travel.qunar.com/travelbook/topic/2812#tm=bmwx1&amp;tf=&amp;in_track=&amp;ex_track=&amp;bd_source=\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#336699;text-decoration:none;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;line-height:normal;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:16px;\">http://travel.qunar.com/travelbook/topic/2812</span></a>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<br />\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"block\">\r\n				<h3>\r\n					费用不包含\r\n				</h3>\r\n				<div class=\"cf\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#003399;\">不包含：</span></strong>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#003399;\">- 行程中产生的燃油费、路桥费、停车费以及因违反交通法规产生的罚款等费用</span></strong>\r\n					</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#003399;\">- 不计免赔服务（如您需要，可在租车时向租车供应商预订）</span></strong>\r\n					</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"block \" id=\"js_fee_desc\">\r\n				<h3>\r\n					费用说明\r\n				</h3>\r\n				<div placeholder=\"content\">\r\n					本产品为每间房价格，单人入住，差价不退\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"js_route\">\r\n	<div class=\"bluetitle\">\r\n		<span class=\"narrow\"></span><b>线路特色</b>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"det_l_content\">\r\n		<div class=\"route block\">\r\n			<div>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【宝马 BMW X1 悦驾之旅】双人价！去哪儿网携手BMW推出X1悦驾之旅，全程使用BMW X1最新车型，让您在领略旅途风光同时，尽享BMW带来的操控乐趣；支持多种目的地提车模式，包括目的地机场提车和市内提车，实现旅程中的无缝对接。</strong></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"><strong><img src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/fe/d3/bb/04ce49624ca61123ded9d09715.jpg_92.jpg\" style=\"display:inline;\" data-lazy=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/fe/d3/bb/04ce49624ca61123ded9d09715.jpg_92.jpg\" data-ke-data-lazy=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/fe/d3/bb/04ce49624ca61123ded9d09715.jpg_92.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/67/80/94/5d05b1e75fcff7eb4e59813b3c.jpg_92.jpg\" style=\"display:inline;\" data-lazy=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/67/80/94/5d05b1e75fcff7eb4e59813b3c.jpg_92.jpg\" data-ke-data-lazy=\"http://img1.qunarzz.com/vc/67/80/94/5d05b1e75fcff7eb4e59813b3c.jpg_92.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"color:#555555;font-family:arial, simsun, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"><strong></strong></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<br />\r\n				</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"bluetitle\">\r\n	<span class=\"narrow\"></span><b>产品详情</b>\r\n</div>\r\n<span class=\"tra_p\">共<em>1</em>个酒店套餐可选</span> \r\n<h3 class=\"type_2\">\r\n	酒店介绍\r\n</h3>\r\n<h4>\r\n	酒店1：<em>三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店</em> <b>五星级</b> \r\n</h4>\r\n<div class=\"hotel_home_sort\">\r\n	<span class=\"item\"><em class=\"sort\">房型</em>:双人间&nbsp;&nbsp;园景房&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> <span class=\"item\"><em class=\"sort\">床型</em>:大/双床</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店位于海南省三亚市亚龙湾国家旅游度假区，是由北京今典集团投资，美国SASAKI公司设计的一家以中国唯一具\r\n巴厘岛热带风情为特点的纯度假酒店。\r\n三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店拥有各类豪华客房，其中近70%的客房可将碧蓝辽阔的海景尽收眼底。中、西、泰、韩餐厅提供各类美食供您品尝。您可在坐落于静谧\r\n湖畔的水疗中心享受中西合璧的不同按摩和水疗服务；260米长的洁白沙滩和不同功能的户外泳池，为您提供各类水上运动。酒店拥有亚龙湾最大户外宴会场地，\r\n三块独立临海大草坪可容纳3000人户外草坪宴会。975平方米的无柱大宴会厅可同时容纳1200人，并可自由组合分隔。所有会议厅及多功能厅均配有先进\r\n的视听设备，高速宽带上网功能及多声道同声传译系统。\r\n自开业以来，三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店先后成功地接待了第55届世界小姐总决赛国际媒体组织和部分赛事活动、第14届金鸡百花电影节暨中国电影百年庆典活\r\n动和央视《艺术人生》栏目录制致敬---中国电影等，受到国内外人士的一致好评。2006年9月，酒店成为三亚世界第一大力士冠军赛唯一指定参赛选手和电\r\n视制作团队接待酒店。2008年，酒店作为博鳌亚洲论坛政要接待酒店之一，接待了巴基斯坦总统和斯里兰卡总理。同年酒店还作为奥运迎圣火首传仪式的举办\r\n地，接待了众多名流、明星。酒店连续五次荣获金枕头奖“十大最受欢迎度假酒店”称号。\r\n</div>', '12月06日、12月07日、12月08日等', '5580', '三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店Y', '海南', '9980', ' 3天 2晚', '/lvyou/upload/temp/e5e51362d9446f28ffffffffc8d65eac.jpg_r_390x260x90_a0412334.jpg', '宝马 BMW X1 悦驾之旅】双人价！三亚亚龙湾红树林度假酒店园景客房3天2晚自驾游');
INSERT INTO `xianlu` VALUES ('7', '南宁', '线路说明了啊啊啊', '2018-02-18', '1900', '大巴', '桂林', '2100', '两周三天', '/lvyou/upload/temp/2b76ab286adc45d8bc81e7a3b7700a1d_C_350_230.jpg', '广西北海旅游了');
INSERT INTO `xianlu` VALUES ('8', '宁波', '<div class=\"tc_item_li\" style=\"padding:15px 0px;margin:0px;font-family:Arial, &quot;line-height:18px;border-bottom:1px solid #E3E3E3;color:#333333;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<p class=\"tc_item_p\" style=\"padding:15px 0px 15px 29px;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:15px;line-height:24px;border-left:1px dashed #E9E9E9;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		&nbsp;古北水镇司马台京郊一品农家院位于司马台长城脚下汤河??水畔（小岭6-4），依山傍水，环境优美，是休闲旅游的首选之地。特别是暑夏季节，舒适的山水环境让紧张、繁忙的都市客人暇意不绝。亦可住在好客的云舍农家院，又可品尝河里的鲜鱼鲜虾，真可谓人间蓬莱。汤河蜿蜒流淌，游人可在河中游泳，摸鱼、抓虾，那又是一番郊野情趣。夜幕降临，精心规划的古村泛光夜景超凡脱俗，冷峻中透出丝丝温馨。不论是构思的精巧还是气势的宏大，都堪称国内首屈一指。绝对是不容错过的美景。<img alt=\"QQ截图20151130110309.jpg\" src=\"http://img.52njl.net/Image/bj/shanghu/2015/11/e95974fc418e4337a4e57beb6a57d46c.jpg\" title=\"QQ截图20151130110309.jpg\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;line-height:21px;border-width:initial;border-style:none;list-style:none;vertical-align:middle;display:block;width:600px !important;\" /><img alt=\"QQ截图20151130110322.jpg\" src=\"http://img.52njl.net/Image/bj/shanghu/2015/11/1816030abda343b393b58a7c535e033f.jpg\" title=\"QQ截图20151130110322.jpg\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;line-height:21px;border-width:initial;border-style:none;list-style:none;vertical-align:middle;display:block;width:600px !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"tc_item_li\" style=\"padding:15px 0px;margin:0px;font-family:Arial, &quot;line-height:18px;border-bottom:1px solid #E3E3E3;color:#333333;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"tc_item_litit\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;line-height:18px;overflow:hidden;\">\r\n		<span class=\"i5\" style=\"padding:0px 5px 0px 0px;margin:0px 20px 0px 0px;text-align:right;line-height:28px;float:left;background:url(&quot;width:68px;height:26px;display:block;color:#FF9B26;font-weight:bolder;font-size:16px;\">住宿</span>\r\n		<p style=\"padding:0px 10px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:26px;position:relative;color:#999999;font-size:14px;border:1px solid #E9E9E9;float:left;border-radius:4px;\">\r\n			京郊一品\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p class=\"tc_item_p\" style=\"padding:15px 0px 15px 29px;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-left:15px;line-height:24px;border-left:1px dashed #E9E9E9;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\">\r\n		房间配套设施：电视、空调、WiFi、24小时热水、拖鞋、洗簌用品；床单一换一洗，房间干净舒适。<br style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;line-height:21px;\" />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.52njl.net/Image/yuantu/guanggao/2015/11/20151125104049766780.jpg\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;line-height:21px;border-width:initial;border-style:none;list-style:none;vertical-align:middle;display:block;width:600px !important;\" /><img src=\"http://img.52njl.net/Image/yuantu/guanggao/2015/11/20151125104053910894.jpg\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;line-height:21px;border-width:initial;border-style:none;list-style:none;vertical-align:middle;display:block;width:600px !important;\" /><img src=\"http://img.52njl.net/Image/yuantu/guanggao/2015/11/20151125104057221268.jpg\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px 0px;line-height:21px;border-width:initial;border-style:none;list-style:none;vertical-align:middle;display:block;width:600px !important;\" />\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', '12月04日、12月05日、12月06日等', '2000', '飞机去09:05飞机回15:45', '海南、陵水、三亚', '2000', '5天 4晚', '/lvyou/upload/temp/20161121101748783539.jpg', '京郊一品农家院');
INSERT INTO `xianlu` VALUES ('9', '上海', '<div class=\"product-detail-instance\" id=\"product-detail\" style=\"margin:0px 59px;padding:30px 0px 0px;color:#666666;font-family:Arial, &quot;font-size:12px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n	<ul style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;list-style-type:none;\">\r\n		<div style=\"margin:0px auto;padding:0px;font-family:&quot;\">\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #E3E3E3;\">\r\n				<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:20px;color:#333333;line-height:20px;\">\r\n					<span style=\"width:88px;float:left;line-height:20px;border-right:1px solid #E3E3E3;\">交通信息</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;height:20px;width:200px;background-image:url(&quot;http://s3.lvjs.com.cn/img/line/product-detail-all.png&quot;background-position:0px -750px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"></span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">\r\n				参考航班1：CZ6782-CZ6781 21:00-00:40/16:45-19:45 浦东T2往返<br />\r\n参考航班2：9C8779-9C8780 06:40-10:00/20:40-23:30 虹桥T1往返<br />\r\n参考航班3：MU5325-MU5326 16:35-20:05/21:05-00:10 浦东T1往返&nbsp;<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:#333333;line-height:24px;\">\r\n				三亚湾希尔顿欢朋酒店\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">\r\n				酒店地址：海南省三亚市天涯区凤凰路凤凰水城169号酒店周边：靠近三亚椰梦长廊、西岛、天涯海角、南山等景区、距三亚凤凰机场约20分钟左右车程，距三亚动车站约10分钟左右车程；&nbsp;<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;font-size:0px;\">\r\n				<span style=\"width:530px;height:353px;margin-right:20px;display:inline-block;\"><img src=\"http://s1.lvjs.com.cn/uploads/pc/place2/2016-07-13/0ca4c25a-3b6d-4870-966d-0d7266d0856b.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"353\" style=\"width:530px;height:353px;\" /></span><span style=\"width:530px;height:353px;margin-right:0px;display:inline-block;\"><img src=\"http://s2.lvjs.com.cn/uploads/pc/place2/2016-07-13/39f39c8e-27fe-46f5-aabc-994b8f840a7a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"353\" style=\"width:530px;height:353px;\" /></span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 15px;padding:0px 0px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid #E3E3E3;\">\r\n				<div style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:20px;color:#333333;line-height:20px;\">\r\n					<span style=\"width:88px;float:left;line-height:20px;border-right:1px solid #E3E3E3;\">景点介绍</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;height:20px;width:200px;background-image:url(&quot;http://s3.lvjs.com.cn/img/line/product-detail-all.png&quot;background-position:0px -669px;background-size:initial;background-repeat:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;\"></span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:#333333;line-height:24px;\">\r\n				蜈支洲岛--AAAA景区\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 10px;padding:0px;font-size:14px;line-height:22px;\">\r\n				景点地址：海南省三亚市海棠湾镇蜈支洲岛景点介绍：美丽的风光，清新的空气，海的颜色真的很漂亮，沙滩洁白而细软，而且岛上还有好玩的水上娱乐项目；&nbsp;<br />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 20px;padding:0px;font-size:0px;\">\r\n				<span style=\"width:530px;height:353px;margin-right:20px;display:inline-block;\"><img src=\"http://s1.lvjs.com.cn/uploads/pc/place2/2016-07-13/fa193f16-4c87-4e44-808a-2a5f3ddea0fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"353\" style=\"width:530px;height:353px;\" /></span><span style=\"width:530px;height:353px;margin-right:0px;display:inline-block;\"><img src=\"http://s2.lvjs.com.cn/uploads/pc/place2/2016-07-13/7c584ca3-973a-4028-b460-c6ce25029aaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"530\" height=\"353\" style=\"width:530px;height:353px;\" /></span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px 0px 6px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:#333333;line-height:24px;\">\r\n				呀诺达--AAAAA景区\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div style=\"margin:0px